Description:Test puzzle for replaying a mana loop from the commander combo list: Bloom Tender plus Freed from the Real. Freed from the Real is already attached to Bloom Tender, and Raging Goblin supplies a red permanent. Record one cycle that taps Bloom Tender for mana and untaps it with Freed from the Real. Repeat to build enough red mana, then cast Banefire targeting the opponent.

